data.description: Nestled on a quiet, dead-end street is the gem that you have been looking for! Step inside to this open-concept floor plan featuring neutral colors, tons of natural light, double trey ceilings in the living room, scratch and water resistant wood flooring and SO much more. This kitchen is an entertainers dream and features a large center island, solid wood & soft close cabinetry, granite countertops and plenty of pantry space! Head out back and take in the sounds and sights of this peaceful, fenced in lot. The backyard is so spacious and the possibilities are endless! This home has been meticulously maintained and is a must-see!
